Name: Average time for Completed + Cancelled across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time it takes Completed + Cancelled to be done after Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total resolution time of Completed + Cancelled when preceded by Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to Completed + Cancelled in variants containing both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time for Completed + Cancelled compared to the average time for Completed + Resolved in identical process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between Completed + In Call and Completed + Cancelled in cases where both occur
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time it takes Completed + Cancelled to be done after Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time for Completed + Cancelled in variants that include Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time until Completed + Cancelled is performed starting from case creation (first event timestamp)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Time of Completed + Cancelled when it directly follows Accepted + In Progress without intermediate waiting states
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time from Completed + In Call to Completed + Cancelled grouped by country
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + Wait - Customer and Completed + Cancelled
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Cycle Time of Completed + Cancelled in variants that originate with Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
